Class DefaultOutputFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.unex.sextante.core.OutputFactory
      • org.gvsig.geoprocess.lib.sextante.core.DefaultOutputFactory

  • public class DefaultOutputFactory
extends es.unex.sextante.core.OutputFactory
    An OutputFactory based on the gvSIG data model. Supports only file-based outputs.

      • getRasterLayerOutputExtensions

        public String[] getRasterLayerOutputExtensions()
        Description copied from class: es.unex.sextante.core.OutputFactory
        Returns the extensions supported by this factory for creating raster layers. If a filename with an extension not found in this list of extensions is used to create a raster layer, the default extension (the first one of the list) will be added to the filename when creating that layer.
        Specified by:
        getRasterLayerOutputExtensions in class es.unex.sextante.core.OutputFactory
        Returns:
        the list of supported extensions for raster layers

      • getDefaultCRS

        public Object getDefaultCRS()
        Description copied from class: es.unex.sextante.core.OutputFactory
        Returns the default CRS for new layers. This will be used when the geoalgorithm generates new layers but does not take any other layer as input, so the CRS cannot be defined from the inputs
        Specified by:
        getDefaultCRS in class es.unex.sextante.core.OutputFactory
        Returns:
        an object containing information about the default CRS (i.e. a String with the EPSG code of the CRS)
